data.description: New listing in the Timberline golf community!  This well maintained home built in 2018 is waiting on you!  On the peaceful street of Medinah Dr, 1054 Medinah features 4 spacious bedrooms 2.5 baths and an amazing open layout from the kitchen onto the living room.  Some of the bells and whistles includes, granite counters, updated flooring, recessed lighting, a flat backyard and lots of natural light.  This home is a must see and priced right, just for you.  Don't miss your opportunity to view!  Stay cool and hydrated!
